    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Game sets in which economics, trading, business and making money are central. Many of these games use dice to determine movement of players across a board, such as in the game of Monopoly.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
